<i>adjective</i>: 경멸스럽다 [경멸스럽따] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>adjective</i><br>
<dt>경멸스럽다 [경멸스럽따]</dt><br>
<dd>contemptuous; contemptible</dd><br>
<dd>무시하거나 낮추어 보고 싶을 만큼 매우 싫다.</dd><br>
<dd>Hating someone so much that one wants to ignore or look down on the person.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>